cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG AMF interface IP to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet, will cause unreachable routing and prevent NG interface connectivity.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 NG AMF 介面 IP 設定為 '10.0.0.1'，該地址位於不同子網中，會導致無法到達的路由，並阻止 NG 介面連線。

du.explanation_en: Changing Ta4 timing parameter from [110,180] to [180,110] creates an invalid range where the upper bound is less than the lower bound, causing timing misalignment and front-haul synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Ta4 時序參數從 [110,180] 更改為 [180,110] 會建立無效範圍，其中上限小於下限，導致時序錯位和前傳同步失敗。
